description: Separated from her precious Kardunn, Maya has been forcibly enrolled into the Creator Academy, run by a shrewd and mysterious ex-Creator named Morgan Etain. While attempting to make friends and find a positive side to this new life, Maya realizes that she may be in way over her head, surrounded by other Creators who all come from difficult and traumatic backgrounds.
